caption.p: Inhibition of CET activity in different serotypes of dengue virus. (A–D) Effects of CET treatment on DENV1-4. The anti-dengue ability of CET was determined using qRT-PCR. The data shown here represent the mean and SD. Statistical significance was determined via a t-test compared with each dengue virus group: * indicates p < 0.05, ** indicates p < 0.01, *** indicates p < 0.001.
